303→            secman - Security Requirement and Risk Assessment Management CLI
304→
305→            Usage: secman <command> [options]
306→                   secman help <command>       Show detailed help for a command
307→
308→            Commands:
309→              CrowdStrike:
310→                query                  Query CrowdStrike vulnerabilities for a single host
311→                query servers          Batch query and import server vulnerabilities
312→                monitor                Continuously monitor for HIGH/CRITICAL vulnerabilities
313→                config                 Configure CrowdStrike API credentials
314→
315→              Notifications:
316→                send-notifications     Send email notifications for outdated assets
317→                send-admin-summary     Send system statistics summary email to ADMIN users
318→
319→              User & Access Management:
320→                manage-user-mappings   Manage user mappings for domains and AWS accounts
321→                manage-workgroups      Manage workgroup asset assignments (list, assign, remove)
322→
323→              Vulnerabilities:
324→                add-vulnerability      Add or update a vulnerability for an asset
325→                deduplicate-vulnerabilities  Remove duplicate vulnerability records (ADMIN)
326→
327→              Requirements:
