388→                  --save                   Save asset and vulnerabilities to database (direct access)
389→                  --verbose                Enable verbose logging
390→
391→                Examples:
392→                  secman query --hostname server01
393→                  secman query --hostname server01 --severity CRITICAL --verbose
394→                  secman query --hostname server01 --severity HIGH,CRITICAL --save
